<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="29Jan1931"><font color="red">29 January 1931</font> <i>BLHW</i> (Stuart Gilbert to Harriet Weaver): Mr Joyce asks me to transmit a brief communiqu&eacute; &hellip; He has been suffering from rather acute insomnia lately &hellip; I&apos;m glad to say Work in Progress is again in progress. Just now I&apos;ve been reading to him long medieval homilies on angels (and devils), the gist of which will enter into the &ldquo;Children&apos;s Games&rdquo; section of W. in P. Others also are assisting, I hear </div>
